'''托马斯·霍恩'''（Thomas Horn，{{bd|1997年|12月14日}}）<ref name=rvdc>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cinemareview.com/castcrew.asp?id=6079 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2012-02-06 |archive-date=2012-10-05 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BBiUWlrK?url=http://www.cinemareview.com/castcrew.asp?id=6079 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>是一名美国儿童演员，主演了2011年电影《[[心靈鑰匙|心靈鑰匙]]》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/movies/2012/01/stephen-daldry-martin-scorsese-george-clooney-directors-roundtable-working-with-kids.html |title=Stephen Daldry: Young Thomas Horn is 'a proper leading man' - latimes.com |publisher=Latimesblogs.latimes.com |date= |accessdate=2012-01-22 |archive-date=2012-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120314072005/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/movies/2012/01/stephen-daldry-martin-scorsese-george-clooney-directors-roundtable-working-with-kids.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2010年，他在《[[危险边缘|危险边缘]]》节目中赢得了$31,800，观看节目的制片人[[Scott_Rudin|Scott Rudin]]被他的表现打动，因此主动联系他出演Oskar Schell这个角色<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/story/2011-12-22/thomas-horn-extremely-loud-and-incredibly-close/52172690/1 |title=Thomas Horn got big break from 'Jeopardy!' – |publisher=Usatoday.com |date= |accessdate=2012-01-22 |archive-date=2012-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120228152619/http://www.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/story/2011-12-22/thomas-horn-extremely-loud-and-incredibly-close/52172690/1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

他生于[[加州|加州]][[旧金山|旧金山]]，是[[克罗地亚|克罗地亚]]裔美国人，能熟练讲[[克罗地亚语|克罗地亚语]]，会讲一些[[西班牙语|西班牙语]]，并已经学习[[普通话|普通话]]两年时间<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fc%2Fa%2F2012%2F01%2F15%2FPK5D1MKVEM.DTL |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-10-05 |archive-date=2012-10-05 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BBiVKzzM?url=http://www.sfgate.com/movies/article/Thomas-Horn-s-incredibly-fast-start-to-career-2494262.php |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mercurynews.com/entertainment/ci_19732926 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2012-02-06 |archive-date=2012-10-05 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BBiWNocI?url=http://www.mercurynews.com/entertainment/ci_19732926 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.post-gazette.com/pg/12020/1204674-120.stm |title=存档副本 |access-date=2012-02-06 |archive-date=2012-10-05 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BBiXUQ2r?url=http://www.post-gazette.com/stories/ae/movie-reviews/911-aftermath-drama-extremely-loud-incredibly-close-tugs-at-heartstrings-218443/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

